title: LF any active ranked team
body:
Im an experienced player of ranked 5's whos mains jg but can fill any role. Im only gold 5 but alot better than that looking for any active ranked team to play with check my soloq stats. Keen to join a new active ranked team to help them and myself and improve. Feel free to add me and message me.

IGN: Matt 1000

replies.body:
>im only gold 5 but alot better than that 

Let's keep it real, bro - if you're gold 5, that's the level at which you're at. You're not a Plat/Diamond level player. You're barely even Gold-level, given that you're in divison 5.  Be honest with yourself. It's nothing to be ashamed of - after all, you're relatively new to the game.
